<http://www.w3.org/ns/adms#last> <http://www.w3.org/1999/02/22-rdf-syntax-ns#type> <http://www.w3.org/2002/07/owl#ObjectProperty> .
<http://www.w3.org/ns/adms#last> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#label> "last"@en .
<http://www.w3.org/ns/adms#last> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#comment> "A link to the current or latest version of the Asset."@en .
