<http://www.w3.org/ns/adms#prev> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#isDefinedBy> <http://www.w3.org/ns/adms> .
<http://www.w3.org/ns/adms#prev> <http://www.w3.org/1999/02/22-rdf-syntax-ns#type> <http://www.w3.org/2002/07/owl#ObjectProperty> .
<http://www.w3.org/ns/adms#prev> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#label> "prev"@en .
<http://www.w3.org/ns/adms#prev> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#comment> "A link to the previous version of the Asset."@en .
<http://www.w3.org/ns/adms#prev> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#domain> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#Resource> .
