<http://www.w3.org/ns/adms#representationTechnique> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#isDefinedBy> <http://www.w3.org/ns/adms> .
<http://www.w3.org/ns/adms#representationTechnique> <http://www.w3.org/1999/02/22-rdf-syntax-ns#type> <http://www.w3.org/2002/07/owl#ObjectProperty> .
<http://www.w3.org/ns/adms#representationTechnique> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#label> "representation technique"@en .
<http://www.w3.org/ns/adms#representationTechnique> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#comment> "More information about the format in which an Asset Distribution is released. This is different from the file format as, for example, a ZIP file (file format) could contain an XML schema (representation technique)."@en .
<http://www.w3.org/ns/adms#representationTechnique> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#domain> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#Resource> .
<http://www.w3.org/ns/adms#representationTechnique> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#range> <http://www.w3.org/2004/02/skos/core#Concept> .
