<http://www.w3.org/ns/adms#status> <http://www.w3.org/1999/02/22-rdf-syntax-ns#type> <http://www.w3.org/2002/07/owl#ObjectProperty> .
<http://www.w3.org/ns/adms#status> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#label> "status"@en .
<http://www.w3.org/ns/adms#status> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#comment> "The status of the Asset in the context of a particular workflow process."@en .
