<http://www.w3.org/ns/adms#supportedSchema> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#label> "supported schema"@en .
<http://www.w3.org/ns/adms#supportedSchema> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#comment> "A schema according to which the Asset Repository can provide data about its content, e.g. ADMS."@en .
