<http://www.w3.org/ns/adms#translation> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#label> "translation"@en .
<http://www.w3.org/ns/adms#translation> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#comment> "Links Assets that are translations of each other."@en .
